# ── Real UPI payouts (Razorpay / RazorpayX) ──────────────────────────────
# Requires RazorpayX to be approved + KYC'd + funded on your account —
# this is a business/compliance step only you can do, no code can skip it.
# Get keys from: https://dashboard.razorpay.com → Settings → API Keys
# Get account number from: RazorpayX dashboard → your virtual account
RAZORPAY_KEY_ID=
RAZORPAY_KEY_SECRET=
RAZORPAY_ACCOUNT_NUMBER=
